        settled\r\n1029        3290643         422.500      USD       2023-10-28         purchase           settled\r\n5198        3294415         101.450      EUR       2023-11-20         purchase           settled\r\n4630        3294415         103.681      EUR       2023-11-20         purchase           settled\r\n7520        3369036          16.070      GBP       2023-12-11         purchase          declined\r\n2906        3369036          15.951      GBP       2023-12-11         purchase          declined\r\n6221        3394968          16.313      EUR       2023-11-20         purchase           settled\r\n3300        3394968          17.120      EUR       2023-11-20         purchase           settled\r\n3315        3407851         119.994      EUR       2023-10-30         purchase           settled\r\n1709        3407851         115.210      EUR       2023-10-30         purchase           settled\r\n5370        3564645          38.118      NGN       2023-12-21         purchase           settled\r\n2966        3564645          39.070      NGN       2023-12-21         purchase           settled\r\n1829        3571889         107.950      USD       2023-10-03         purchase           settled\r\n3618        3571889         108.870      USD       2023-10-03         purchase           settled\r\n"]
